@startuml TeleScent ML Pipeline Simple
!theme cyborg
skinparam backgroundColor #1E1E1E
skinparam defaultFontColor #FFFFFF
title <color:#FFFFFF>TeleScent ML Pipeline</color>

skinparam rectangle {
    roundCorner 8
    FontColor #FFFFFF
    FontSize 12
}

skinparam arrow {
    Color #9E9E9E
    FontColor #FFFFFF
    FontSize 11
}

' Simple linear flow
rectangle "**IoT Sensors**\nESP32\n6 Gas Sensors" as sensors #4A148C
rectangle "**Data Collection**\nLabeled Samples\n5 Scent Classes" as data #4A148C
rectangle "**Model Training**\nRandom Forest\n95%+ Accuracy" as training #1B5E20
rectangle "**Saved Models**\n6-Sensor Full\n2-Sensor Simple" as models #4A3200
rectangle "**Real-Time Inference**\nserve.py\n<50ms Response" as inference #1E3A5F

' Linear flow
sensors -right-> data : "Stream\nData"
data -right-> training : "Train"
training -right-> models : "Save"
models -right-> inference : "Load"
sensors -down-> inference : "Predict"

note bottom
  <b>Key Features:</b>
  • 6-sensor array (VOC, NOx, NO2, Ethanol, etc.)
  • Random Forest classifier (200 trees)
  • 95-98% accuracy | <50ms inference
  • Dual models: Full (6-sensor) & Simple (2-sensor)
  • Auto-detects available sensors
end note

@enduml
